Current members

* Keisuke Kuwata – vocals, guitar (1977–1985, 1988–2000, 2003–2008, 2013–present)
* Kazuyuki Sekiguchi – bass (1977–1985, 1988–1991, 1995–2000, 2003–2008, 2013–present)
* – drums (1977–1985, 1988–2000, 2003–2008, 2013–present)
* Yuko Hara – keyboards, vocals (1977–1985, 1988–2000, 2003–2008, 2013–present)
* – percussion (1977–1985, 1988–2000, 2003–2008, 2013–present)

Former members

 – guitar (1977–1985, 1988–2000)

